hwWlanStation.name: hwWlanStation

revisions.description: V1.14, Modify the description of hwWlanStaStatOperMode and hwWlanStaApId.
V1.13, Add the nodes ofhwWlanStaGetIPFailedCount and hwWlanStaGetIPSuccessCount.
V1.12, Modify the nodes of hwWlanStaAssocStartTime, hwWlanStaAssocSuccessTime and so on.
V1.11, Add the node of hwWlanStaRoamTraceEntry in the hwWlanStaRoamTraceInfo.
V1.10, Add the node of hwWlanStaAcL3RoamStatisticAcDescription in the hwWlanStaAcL3RoamStatisticsTable.
V1.09, Add the nodes of hwWlanStaVHTCapable,hwWlanStaVHTTxBFCapable,hwWlanStaMUMIMOCapable, hwWlanStaWpaStartTime and hwWlanStaWpaSuccessTime in the hwWlanStationTable.
V1.08, Add the nodes of hwWlanStaAssocStartTime,hwWlanStaAssocSuccesTime,hwWlanStaAuthStartTime, hwWlanStaAuthSuccesTime,hwWlanStaDhcpStartTime and hwWlanStaDhcpSuccesTime in the hwWlanStationTable.
V1.07, Add the nodes of hwWlanStationApStatApId in the hwWlanStationApStatTable.
V1.06, Add the nodes of hwWlanStationUapsdCapacity and hwWlanStationPowerSavePercent in the hwWlanStationTable.
V1.05, Add Value list in the hwWlanStaAuthenMethod node.
V1.04, Add AP ID in the trap node.
The MIB module defines the station operation.
V1.02, Add the node of hwWlanStaApId in the hwWlanStationTable.
V1.01, Add the description of mib nodes.

hwWlanStaAccessTime.name: hwWlanStaAccessTime
hwWlanStaAccessTime.description: This object indicates the time when user authentication starts.If non-authentication is configured, the value of this object is equal to hwStaAssociateTime. If other authentication modes, especially, Portal authentication, are configured, the value of this object is larger than hwStaAssociateTime.

hwWlanStaOnlineTime.name: hwWlanStaOnlineTime
hwWlanStaOnlineTime.description: This object indicates the association time of the STA (online time), which is timed from the first association.The unit is second. 1:When the STA switches another AP, the online time is not cleared, and is accumulated. 2: When the STA is disassociated from the AP, the STA data is cleared. New statistics of the STA will be collected when the STA goes online the next time.

hwWlanStaAccessOnlineTime.name: hwWlanStaAccessOnlineTime
hwWlanStaAccessOnlineTime.description: This object indicates the time elapsed since the user passes the authentication. This object applies only to Portal authentication users.
